      children: "The statue was constructed at a cost of US$47 million by Aerosun Corporation of Nanjing, China, while the total cost of the entire project is well over US$100 million. Names of sponsors are displayed in the meditation hall which forms the throne of the Great Buddha Dordenma."
    }, void 0, false, {
